question: Which reservoir in Clinton, Massachusetts is the biggest?
sql:
SELECT *, ST_Area(lakes.geometry::geography) AS computed_area FROM lakes
WHERE water = 'reservoir'
AND ST_Intersects(lakes.geometry::geography, ST_GeomFromText('POLYGON ((-71.718362 42.41022, -71.688191 42.436744, -71.656741 42.430957, -71.660634 42.418232, -71.668069 42.394566, -71.676516 42.396118, -71.678766 42.389163, -71.701032 42.395805, -71.72598 42.390289, -71.721579 42.409239, -71.718362 42.41022))',4326)::geography)
ORDER BY computed_area DESC
LIMIT 1;
